ex04: Lighting and Textures

Willem A. (Vlakkies) Schreuder
CSCI4239/5239 Spring 2026

Demonstrates different lighting models.


Key bindings
  m          Toggle shaders
  o          Change objects
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
